<topic id="whr-search-template">
  <title>Search Results Layout Page</title>
  <body>
    <p>This layout page is used to generate HTML pages that present search results in the WebHelp
      Responsive output. The name of the template file is <filepath>wt_search.html</filepath> and it
      is located in the following directory: </p>
    <codeblock outputclass="language-ini"><term keyref="glossentry_dita_ot_dir"/>/plugins/<abbreviated-form keyref="glossentry-wh-plugin-dir"/>/templates/dita/bootstrap/</codeblock>
    <p>The HTML page that is produced consists of a search results component along with various
      other additional components, such as a title, menu, or index link.</p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <title>Examples of Search Results Page Components</title>
        <image href="../img/webhelp_search_page.PNG" id="image_ic2_2mp_kv" placement="inline"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>The components that can be referenced in the <filepath>wt_search.html</filepath> template
      file are as follows:</p>
    <ul id="ul_jc2_2mp_kv">
      <li><xref
          href="webhelp_template_components.dita#webhelp_template_components/section_publication_title"
            ><ph conkeyref="reusable-webhelp-customizing/wh_publication_title"></ph></xref></li>
